      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a mechanic's project or a parts donor. The engine is currently not running and will require significant internal repairs or a total replacement to be roadworthy again. Externally, there is visible rust perforation on the rear quarter panels and several large scuffs on the bumpers. The interior has seen better days, with significant tearing on the driver's seat and a headliner that is starting to sag, so please expect a full restoration project.",
